OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome low cloud around this
OL,6,Fmorning, possibly some mist and fog
OL,7,Fpatches too, eventually clearing to a
OL,8,Fbright day in the east. Thicker cloud
OL,9,Fwill continue to push in from the
OL,10,Fwest, with some spots of drizzle
OL,11,Faround hills. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSimilar overnight. Often
OL,14,Fcloudy, breezy with spells of rain and
OL,15,Fdrizzle, often the most persistent
OL,16,Facross any high ground. Another mild
OL,17,Fnight to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
