OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry start to the
OL,6,Fday, perhaps some lingering drizzle
OL,7,Faround hills, gradually turning wet
OL,8,Fand windy through the day, with some
OL,9,Fheavy rain possible. Temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining above average.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,13,Fwith further rain at times on Friday.
OL,14,FDrier and perhaps brighter on Saturday
OL,15,Fbefore further rain arrives later and
OL,16,Finto Sunday. Often windy with
OL,17,Ftemperatures returning to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
